org.sbml.jsbml.validator.offline.constraints

Class AbstractConstraint<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.validator.offline.constraints.AbstractConstraint<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnyConstraint<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstraintGroup, ValidationConstraint

    public abstract class AbstractConstraint<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AnyConstraint<T>
    Abstract generic mother class for all the constraints. It provides a basic implementation of AnyConstraint.getErrorCode().

    Subclasses should set their own id by calling AbstractConstraint(int).

    Since:
    1.2
